Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-35,0:00:-02.-76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-74,0:00:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zenny of the Island of Goats and\Nthe Pirate Ship In the Mountains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them! Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I thought they were these great pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but these fainthearted guys are\Njust running away, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, let's be the ones who\Nbring in the Straw Hat pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring them in, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! If we don't do something,\Nthey really will hit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, these navy guys are pesky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you caught anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of catching something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single drop of water left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're either going\Nto shrivel up, or die of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan, it's time for afternoon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care for some\Nmille-feuille, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, mister cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a snack, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, where the hell did\Nyou have that hidden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys keep your mitts off of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the lack of a sense of urgency?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time to be laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, this sea looks even\Nmore alarming than the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your navigating skills and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to use this\Nfog to give the navy the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this water is moving fast.\NWhat's more, there are reefs everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This region of the ocean is designated\Nas a class-one danger zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuing them any farther is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, we'll be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! We've chased them this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've almost got them, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, let's finish this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw. Come about at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got orders from Captain Moore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that once we spot the Straw Hat pirates,\Nwe are to eliminate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pestering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is not in command\Nright now. I am. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard aport! Pull the sail 45° to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, an island! I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it has something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six people and one animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter how many\Nof you damn pirates there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's uninhabited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A goat?\N--M-Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat! Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I don't care how hungry you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't just go after that cute little goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the cute little goats\Nhave taken a liking to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap! We've fallen into their trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cut them, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren't bad! I can tell that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabasco Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The goat kicked it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We're not going to eat\Nyou or anything! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you all set a trap for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They were ordered by somebody to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Keep out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird old man fell out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, is this the man who\Ngave the goats their orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have thought we\Nwere here to attack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We just want\Nsome water and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I trust anything a pirate says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you right now, there's no\Ntreasure on this island, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am penniless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very rich, in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn pirates! If that's how you\Nwant it, I'll be a man about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simmer me, bake me, do whatever you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I'm a cook.\NSimmering and baking are my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! I was just joking!\NYou fiend! You scoundrel! You killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone limp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's grit is amazing,\Nbut he's pretty fainthearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! His heart has stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro!\N--You ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How cruel!\N--Mossy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hold on, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor! Let's hurry and\Ntake the old man to his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very nearly killed out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't drop your\Nguard around a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to you! You fainted all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old goat man, did your\Nheart stop out of shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here in the Grand Line,\Nthere must be surprises every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you've lasted this long,\Nwith that faint heart of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we're glad that you're life isn't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to be glad about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already scared the hell\Nout of me, and nearly got me killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, now I can't chop\Nfirewood, or draw any water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out a whole bunch, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altogether, I've lost 50,000,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overcharging, aren't you?\NAt the most, it should be this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're being stingy!\NEven with a huge discount, it's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you subtract Chopper's\Nconsultation fee, it's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you young folks ganging up\Nto pick on an old man like me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not picking on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I can't go on anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, old goat man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll chop your wood\Nand draw your water for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reasonable sort,\Naren't you, my straw-hatted lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old guy sure did seem\Nto dislike pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he has\Nsome grudge against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the old man is\Nthe only person on the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that it's been 20 years since\Nhe washed up here from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've met someone like that before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where are you going, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm going to go look\Nfor something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the old man is going\Nto share anything with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! In that case, get some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask for too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your back into it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you youngsters even\Nchop wood right these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. This cleaning is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do this over, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, get some grass to\Nthe island goats, and fix the hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm so tired... Don't just\Nstand there, rub my shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might pay me a little mind,\Nwithout me having to tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people really are so\Nmuch trouble. After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, which way is north,\Nand which way is south?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old-timer has been pushing\Nwork on us, one job after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship was run down, but it\Nwas definitely a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy is the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the old-timer build a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just might be in luck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, let's go have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it's at the top of the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there's no need to run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! It'll take too long\Nto get there starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it was this close, in a straight line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems creepy somehow, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a ghost ship in the mountains, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, don't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of the dead! Didn't I tell you so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used lumber from the local trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like he stopped midway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy really did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's not here, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my guess is correct, that old man is,\Nin actual fact, a former pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably got shipwrecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll bet he's the only one\Nwho made it to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, he was building this\Npirate ship to get off the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but a former pirate disliking pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't make any sense, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just simple camouflage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep us from finding\Nthe treasure he's hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was shady, right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that furniture in the old man's hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had some pretty valuable\Nthings together there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Nami-san! Very astute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that fainthearted\Nold man was once a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but he might have been\Na famous pirate long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And above all else, there's this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a dense forest ahead, with no paths...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a steep cliff to the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's going to build a boat to escape on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why do it up here in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you turn back?\NA danger zone, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:03.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can fear those,\Nand still preserve the navy's justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry. But it\Nwon't be possible for them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get out of that danger\Nzone so easily, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have gotten too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Smoker, and Hina,\Nleader of the Black Cage Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let the Straw Hat pirates slip away from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we will stop them at\Nmy hand, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be of no matter, once they\Nare within your grasp, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin a search at once! Go locate\Nwhere the Straw Hat pirates are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uh, Captain...\N--Let's go, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you report\Nthat island to the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I saw the island, not recorded\Nanywhere in that area of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep that from the captain\Nfor a little while. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? The Straw Hat pirates\Nare probably on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to let you in on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who put down\NCrocodile in Alabasta was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Captain Smoker, hero of the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That turns out to be the official\Nstatement, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who exactly was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Straw Hat pirates, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we took those guys on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many lives\Nwe had, it wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't believe everything\Nyou hear from the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to fight them head-on,\Nthey'd wipe us out like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind them, I need you to give\Nme a hand with something, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get off this island, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, that funny old man
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is just going to keep slave-driving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm staying here.\N--Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat! I can't fill up on just this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I had to go out looking for that food!\N--For the time being, let's head back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Chopper, we're going back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay by the old man's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just abandon one\Nof my patients, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's gotten better. If you feel\Nsorry for him, there'll be no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man's heart didn't\Nstop just because he's timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So by "there will be an end," you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.\NThat old man only has three days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good morning, old-timer!\N--Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji is a noted cook, so this is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island goats told me where the fruit is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some points where the fishing was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chan, I'm warning you,\NI don't have a penny to pay with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's fishy here. Way too fishy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a proverb about this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beware of pirates that suddenly become nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any poison in this, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to be kind\Nto the elderly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want any, I'll eat it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'm eating, I'm eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, don't startle him!\N--Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you've eaten a\NDevil Fruit, too, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! It truly has been a long time\Nsince I've had anything this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, if there's anything we\Ncan do for you, just ask us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't leave behind any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like this kind of food,\NI'll make it for you, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will, huh? Well, thanks.\NWow, this really is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terribly yummy.\NThis goes beyond yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, old goat man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't tell me...!\N--It's happening already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no!\N--Hey, stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! It was so good,\NI rushed through eating it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got it stuck in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your food got stuck in your throat, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure it was too soon for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too soon for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing at all! He means\Nyou're eating too quick, old-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind him, have some of mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourself to this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Much obliged, much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His appetite is on the same\Nlevel as Luffy's, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really only have three days left to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the records,\Nthere was a man who fought
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against some pirates in that\Narea of the sea 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hasn't been seen since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now. He was a guy\Nnamed Zenny, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard wasn't the\Nonly thing that went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge treasure disappeared with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposing he made it to that island,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if he has already kicked the bucket...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure doesn't have a\Nlife expectancy, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already eaten too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we going to have\Nto look after the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he's a pirate, or has treasure,\Nit's none of our business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should embrace a more inquisitive mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pursuers from the navy\Nare already that close!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, are you scared?\N--I'm not talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How's Tricks? The Designs\Nof Zenny the Moneylender!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
